HEADWORD: Resurgent
<hw>Re*sur"gent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>resurgens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>resurgere</ets>.
See <er>Resurrection</er>.]</ety> <def>Rising again, as from the
